            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table>
 To create an edge defined Coons surface patch mesh</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Choose Draw &gt; Surfaces
 &gt; Edge Surface
 from the main menu.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the first edge.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the second, third,
 and fourth edges.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
